1
00:01:30,580 --> 00:01:34,990
[Deep Lurk]

2
00:01:35,490 --> 00:01:37,820
[Episode 21]

3
00:01:47,180 --> 00:01:48,380
How can a nurse

4
00:01:48,610 --> 00:01:50,600
have such quick hands?

5
00:01:53,110 --> 00:01:53,870
Old Madam,

6
00:01:54,030 --> 00:01:55,800
by the time you finish embroidering this handkerchief,

7
00:01:55,870 --> 00:01:57,590
Young Master and Miss Mi Lan

8
00:01:57,610 --> 00:01:58,740
might already be engaged.

9
00:01:58,850 --> 00:01:59,979
Engaged?

10
00:02:00,230 --> 00:02:00,910
Yes,

11
00:02:01,510 --> 00:02:02,710
I heard from Dao that

12
00:02:02,830 --> 00:02:04,560
Miss Mi Lan has already agreed.

13
00:02:04,750 --> 00:02:06,670
Young Master is still mourning.

14
00:02:06,790 --> 00:02:08,270
He can't get engaged

15
00:02:08,289 --> 00:02:09,729
or married yet.

16
00:02:09,910 --> 00:02:11,510
But Miss Mi Lan has already agreed.

17
00:02:11,530 --> 00:02:13,290
So isn't it settled?

18
00:02:14,670 --> 00:02:15,630
Mi Lan

19
00:02:15,650 --> 00:02:17,130
makes me feel uneasy.

20
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:19,400
I can't just let Hongqi

21
00:02:19,430 --> 00:02:21,110
marry her like this.

22
00:02:24,590 --> 00:02:25,430
Jingyu,

23
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:27,950
give Mi Lan a call later

24
00:02:28,030 --> 00:02:28,829
and tell her

25
00:02:28,950 --> 00:02:30,630
to come over to our house.

26
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:32,950
I can finish embroidering this handkerchief today.

27
00:02:33,030 --> 00:02:34,150
I want to give it to her.

28
00:02:34,620 --> 00:02:35,150
Alright,

29
00:02:35,190 --> 00:02:35,990
I'll call her right away.

30
00:02:36,870 --> 00:02:37,470
Good.

31
00:02:39,110 --> 00:02:40,660
Are Young Master and Second Young Master at home?

32
00:02:40,829 --> 00:02:42,190
They both left early this morning.

33
00:02:42,220 --> 00:02:44,220
Old Madam hasn't seen them yet today.

34
00:02:44,750 --> 00:02:46,710
If Old Madam called me over alone,

35
00:02:46,870 --> 00:02:48,280
things might be a bit easier to handle.

36
00:02:48,420 --> 00:02:50,650
I can always find a way to dispel her doubts.

37
00:02:51,390 --> 00:02:52,390
I'll play it by ear.

38
00:03:01,670 --> 00:03:02,310
Old Madam,

39
00:03:02,330 --> 00:03:03,500
Miss Mi Lan is here.

40
00:03:03,670 --> 00:03:04,630
Hello, Granny.

41
00:03:05,030 --> 00:03:06,030
Hello, Mi Lan.

42
00:03:06,110 --> 00:03:07,550
Come on, have a seat.

43
00:03:08,950 --> 00:03:09,990
I'll go back to work.

44
00:03:11,540 --> 00:03:12,270
Granny,

45
00:03:12,420 --> 00:03:13,630
you're looking at photos?

46
00:03:13,990 --> 00:03:14,830
Yes,

47
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:16,640
when you get old,

48
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:17,960
you tend to reminisce,

49
00:03:18,060 --> 00:03:20,430
take out photos and look at them from time to time,

50
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:22,920
recalling things from the past.

51
00:03:23,060 --> 00:03:24,329
It's quite interesting.

52
00:03:24,810 --> 00:03:25,930
Look at this one.

53
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:27,240
This is

54
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,900
the first graduating class of the Girls' School

55
00:03:29,930 --> 00:03:31,120
in their graduation photo.

56
00:03:31,590 --> 00:03:32,990
The graduates from this class

57
00:03:33,070 --> 00:03:34,190
are the most successful.

58
00:03:34,270 --> 00:03:36,400
Look at this one, and this one,

59
00:03:36,510 --> 00:03:38,350
and the one standing next to me.

60
00:03:38,510 --> 00:03:39,510
You must know

61
00:03:40,150 --> 00:03:42,030
all these people now.

62
00:03:42,390 --> 00:03:45,710
They're all famous figures in Changsha now.

63
00:03:46,150 --> 00:03:48,470
Their articles are often published in newspapers.

64
00:03:50,390 --> 00:03:51,350
And this one,

65
00:03:51,790 --> 00:03:53,230
this pair of twin sisters.

66
00:03:53,510 --> 00:03:54,510
Do they look alike?

67
00:03:54,850 --> 00:03:55,410
Yes.

68
00:03:55,870 --> 00:03:57,110
Their

69
00:03:57,370 --> 00:04:00,290
interests and hobbies are almost exactly the same.

70
00:04:00,390 --> 00:04:03,750
They even chose the same career path.

71
00:04:04,090 --> 00:04:06,200
Both went into education.

72
00:04:07,150 --> 00:04:07,990
Let me test you.

73
00:04:08,150 --> 00:04:09,580
Guess who they are.

74
00:04:09,870 --> 00:04:11,430
They're very famous.

75
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,330
The Ji sisters?

76
00:04:15,150 --> 00:04:16,029
Correct.

77
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,829
The older sister

78
00:04:18,870 --> 00:04:20,709
is now the Deputy Minister of Education,

79
00:04:20,910 --> 00:04:23,890
and the younger one is the principal of Mingde Primary School.

80
00:04:25,260 --> 00:04:29,780
Both Shen and Hongqi attended Mingde Primary School.

81
00:04:30,950 --> 00:04:33,710
Which primary school did you attend back then?

82
00:04:34,430 --> 00:04:35,840
So she's indeed suspicious of me.

83
00:04:39,190 --> 00:04:40,510
Tea Garden Street Primary School.

84
00:04:41,700 --> 00:04:43,830
Unfortunately, the Wenxi fire

85
00:04:44,290 --> 00:04:47,170
burned the school to the ground.

86
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:52,190
I think I have a photo of your school.

87
00:04:52,670 --> 00:04:53,700
Let me look for it.

88
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,610
Really?

89
00:04:54,630 --> 00:04:55,210
Here it is.

90
00:04:56,510 --> 00:04:57,390
Back then,

91
00:04:57,420 --> 00:05:00,560
our Yun family donated many elementary schools.

92
00:05:01,030 --> 00:05:02,190
This photo

93
00:05:02,310 --> 00:05:03,830
was taken when Hongqi's grandfather

94
00:05:03,950 --> 00:05:07,310
attended your school's opening ceremony.

95
00:05:09,510 --> 00:05:12,740
I remember there was a well at your school.

96
00:05:13,230 --> 00:05:14,750
Do you remember where it was?

97
00:05:16,750 --> 00:05:17,510
The well?

98
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:20,040
Let's look at the photo.

99
00:05:20,070 --> 00:05:21,110
It's interesting.

100
00:05:22,510 --> 00:05:24,310
After the opening ceremony,

101
00:05:24,380 --> 00:05:27,030
he asked me to take a photo of him by this wall.

102
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:28,790
The water from this well

103
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:30,060
was particularly sweet.

104
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:32,990
I remember now.

105
00:05:33,300 --> 00:05:33,980
Yes,

106
00:05:34,260 --> 00:05:35,750
that well at our school.

107
00:05:37,150 --> 00:05:38,310
In the summer,

108
00:05:38,350 --> 00:05:40,110
our teacher always liked to use that well

109
00:05:40,130 --> 00:05:41,390
to cool watermelons for us to eat.

110
00:05:42,110 --> 00:05:43,990
I was too small back then,

111
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:46,340
always losing out to other classmates.

112
00:05:48,350 --> 00:05:51,320
You've grown to just the right height now.

113
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:15,330
[Yun Residence]

114
00:06:30,510 --> 00:06:31,380
Look at me,

115
00:06:31,790 --> 00:06:34,750
I've been going on about my old stories.

116
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:38,070
You probably don't want to hear these things.

117
00:06:38,330 --> 00:06:39,570
I actually enjoy it.

118
00:06:40,630 --> 00:06:41,310
Mi Lan,

119
00:06:41,770 --> 00:06:43,970
your hospital isn't busy today?

120
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:45,760
The hospital isn't too busy.

121
00:06:46,190 --> 00:06:48,909
I have a favor to ask you.

122
00:06:50,710 --> 00:06:51,990
Please, go ahead.

123
00:06:53,610 --> 00:06:54,409
Here's the thing,

124
00:06:55,010 --> 00:06:56,930
the brother-in-law of our hospital's Head Nurse

125
00:06:57,710 --> 00:06:59,110
has been arrested by the NBIS,

126
00:06:59,450 --> 00:07:00,730
and he's fallen ill now,

127
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:01,770
quite seriously.

128
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:05,370
The Head Nurse's cousin wants to go and take care of him,

129
00:07:06,230 --> 00:07:07,950
but the NBIS won't allow it.

130
00:07:09,230 --> 00:07:12,650
Could you talk to Yun Hongshen to help

131
00:07:13,150 --> 00:07:14,910
make an exception?

132
00:07:16,190 --> 00:07:18,630
This is difficult for me.

133
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:21,290
The NBIS has its own discipline.

134
00:07:21,830 --> 00:07:22,790
Besides,

135
00:07:23,110 --> 00:07:26,500
I never interfere in Shen

136
00:07:26,790 --> 00:07:28,550
and Hongqi's affairs.

137
00:07:30,110 --> 00:07:32,550
But you don't need to worry too much.

138
00:07:32,830 --> 00:07:33,790
I'll

139
00:07:34,110 --> 00:07:35,750
ask him in private.

140
00:07:36,270 --> 00:07:38,510
But I'm not sure it'll work.

141
00:07:39,530 --> 00:07:40,330
That's great.

142
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,610
As long as you can ask, Granny,

143
00:07:43,190 --> 00:07:44,270
I'm already very grateful.

144
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,000
Old Madam,

145
00:07:46,070 --> 00:07:47,270
someone from Happy House is here.

146
00:07:47,510 --> 00:07:48,600
Madam Yun,

147
00:07:48,710 --> 00:07:49,870
I've come uninvited.

148
00:07:49,909 --> 00:07:51,110
Please don't mind.

149
00:07:51,490 --> 00:07:52,540
Please, have a seat.

150
00:07:54,940 --> 00:07:55,540
Granny,

151
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:56,550
you have a guest.

152
00:07:56,590 --> 00:07:57,830
I'll go back to work now.

153
00:07:58,230 --> 00:07:59,909
I'll come visit you another day.

154
00:07:59,950 --> 00:08:00,390
Alright.

155
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,510
Goodbye, Granny.

156
00:08:03,310 --> 00:08:03,750
Come.

157
00:08:04,030 --> 00:08:05,030
Old Madam,

158
00:08:05,760 --> 00:08:06,920
this is a prized old

159
00:08:06,950 --> 00:08:08,990
ginseng root from our Boss Bai.

160
00:08:09,230 --> 00:08:10,830
It's excellent for replenishing energy and calming the spirit,

161
00:08:10,950 --> 00:08:13,430
perfect for a long-lived person like you.

162
00:08:13,950 --> 00:08:16,340
If you have something to say, just say it.

163
00:08:33,370 --> 00:08:35,610
Boss Bai was impatient in life,

164
00:08:35,630 --> 00:08:36,630
refusing to admit defeat,

165
00:08:36,950 --> 00:08:38,860
and had offended the Young Master.

166
00:08:39,549 --> 00:08:41,750
I'm here to apologize for him.

167
00:08:42,299 --> 00:08:44,260
Everyone in Changsha knows

168
00:08:44,310 --> 00:08:46,110
that the Old Madam has extraordinary grace.

169
00:08:46,470 --> 00:08:47,590
Please be merciful

170
00:08:47,620 --> 00:08:49,430
and don't hold it against us.

171
00:08:50,950 --> 00:08:52,230
The way you put it,

172
00:08:52,940 --> 00:08:54,790
if I don't show mercy,

173
00:08:55,010 --> 00:08:57,050
then naturally I lack grace.

174
00:08:57,630 --> 00:08:59,030
I didn't mean it.

175
00:08:59,390 --> 00:09:01,150
It's better to resolve conflicts than to create enemies.

176
00:09:01,260 --> 00:09:03,110
More friends mean more opportunities, right?

177
00:09:06,150 --> 00:09:08,340
Our two families are not enemies.

178
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:12,480
We simply have different paths and cannot work together.

179
00:09:13,590 --> 00:09:15,180
We can't be friends either.

180
00:09:15,900 --> 00:09:16,780
Besides,

181
00:09:17,300 --> 00:09:18,660
I never interfere

182
00:09:18,830 --> 00:09:20,470
Hongqi's affairs.

183
00:09:21,110 --> 00:09:23,430
If there's anything you want him to do,

184
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:25,310
you should go to him directly.

185
00:09:25,830 --> 00:09:27,940
Young Master Yun is known for his filial piety.

186
00:09:28,270 --> 00:09:29,550
No matter what it is,

187
00:09:29,750 --> 00:09:31,430
as long as you can ask...

188
00:09:31,540 --> 00:09:32,510
The question is,

189
00:09:32,830 --> 00:09:34,900
why should I ask?

190
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:39,040
I know you have refined tastes

191
00:09:39,070 --> 00:09:40,550
and look down on our line of work.

192
00:09:40,830 --> 00:09:42,630
But times are tough these days;

193
00:09:42,710 --> 00:09:44,590
we're just trying to make a living.

194
00:09:45,350 --> 00:09:46,480
Human trafficking,

195
00:09:46,830 --> 00:09:48,070
smuggling opium,

196
00:09:48,750 --> 00:09:49,910
are these things

197
00:09:50,310 --> 00:09:51,870
just for making a living?

198
00:09:54,350 --> 00:09:55,520
Living in this world,

199
00:09:55,550 --> 00:09:57,000
we're all just seeking wealth.

200
00:09:57,150 --> 00:09:59,110
How the money is earned doesn't matter.

201
00:09:59,150 --> 00:10:00,300
These are just minor details.

202
00:10:00,910 --> 00:10:02,470
If you don't mind,

203
00:10:02,610 --> 00:10:04,030
we could make money together.

204
00:10:09,190 --> 00:10:12,070
You really have no shame, don't you?

205
00:10:13,740 --> 00:10:15,590
Although Happy House has closed,

206
00:10:15,870 --> 00:10:17,830
reopening isn't impossible

207
00:10:17,900 --> 00:10:19,900
if we grease a few palms.

208
00:10:21,390 --> 00:10:23,310
We have the people and the boats.

209
00:10:23,510 --> 00:10:25,590
Your Yun family has the reputation and status.

210
00:10:25,950 --> 00:10:27,310
If our two families join forces,

211
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:29,090
the wealth will surely pour in.

212
00:10:30,710 --> 00:10:31,480
I

213
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:33,800
sincerely want to be friends with you.

214
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,350
If you agree,

215
00:10:37,170 --> 00:10:38,730
I'll give you 30% of the profits.

216
00:10:43,070 --> 00:10:45,120
At most, I can give up another 10%.

217
00:10:45,190 --> 00:10:46,600
If I give up any more than that,

218
00:10:46,640 --> 00:10:48,400
the business won't be viable anymore.

219
00:10:48,990 --> 00:10:52,110
We Yuns are not money-hungry wretches.

220
00:10:53,150 --> 00:10:55,360
We will not discuss this matter any further.

221
00:10:56,230 --> 00:10:57,390
You may leave now.

222
00:10:57,750 --> 00:10:58,750
-Wellâ€¦
-From now on,

223
00:10:59,350 --> 00:11:00,590
you need not come here again.

224
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:02,750
Jingyu,

225
00:11:03,380 --> 00:11:04,510
see the guest out.

226
00:11:17,150 --> 00:11:19,030
The Old Madam of the Yun family is no pushover.

227
00:11:19,710 --> 00:11:21,190
Since she deliberately probed me,

228
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:23,160
she wouldn't have done it for no reason.

229
00:11:24,470 --> 00:11:26,270
There must be a trap in her words.

230
00:11:26,630 --> 00:11:27,550
What could it be?

231
00:11:28,270 --> 00:11:29,710
All my answers were correct

232
00:11:30,170 --> 00:11:31,610
and double-checked.

233
00:11:35,870 --> 00:11:38,590
Which primary school did you attend back then?

234
00:11:45,550 --> 00:11:46,150
Driver,

235
00:11:46,510 --> 00:11:47,600
could you please take me to

236
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:49,070
the former Tea Garden Street Primary School?

237
00:11:49,660 --> 00:11:51,490
Tea Garden Street Primary School burned down long ago.

238
00:11:51,670 --> 00:11:52,670
Why do you want to go there?

239
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,910
I have a friend who used to attend that school.

240
00:11:56,090 --> 00:11:57,390
She asked me to check

241
00:11:57,510 --> 00:11:59,110
if the well in front is still there.

242
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:00,070
Miss,

243
00:12:00,510 --> 00:12:01,590
your friend must be mistaken.

244
00:12:02,070 --> 00:12:04,100
The school with a well in front is Mingde Primary School.

245
00:12:09,180 --> 00:12:10,540
Forget about it.

246
00:12:10,630 --> 00:12:13,270
Please take me back to where I got in earlier.

247
00:12:13,780 --> 00:12:14,470
Alright.

248
00:12:24,350 --> 00:12:24,750
Well...

249
00:12:24,910 --> 00:12:26,350
-Why? Didn't work out?
-Hypocrite.

250
00:12:26,380 --> 00:12:26,870
Let's go.

251
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:36,400
Old Madam.

252
00:12:37,590 --> 00:12:38,230
Jingyu,

253
00:12:38,270 --> 00:12:39,630
go find the Second Young Master quickly,

254
00:12:39,670 --> 00:12:40,870
or ask his colleagues

255
00:12:40,890 --> 00:12:41,930
to tell him to come back immediately.

256
00:12:41,970 --> 00:12:43,090
Alright, I'll go right away.

257
00:12:44,550 --> 00:12:45,500
Principal Wei,

258
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:47,030
is Hongqi there?

259
00:12:47,790 --> 00:12:49,320
Could you please help me find him?

260
00:12:49,390 --> 00:12:51,380
I have an emergency and need him to come home now.

261
00:12:52,430 --> 00:12:53,230
Okay, thank you.

262
00:13:06,870 --> 00:13:07,390
Madam,

263
00:13:07,520 --> 00:13:09,110
the team protecting the Yun family

264
00:13:09,130 --> 00:13:09,830
has sent a message,

265
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:11,080
saying Madam Yun wants us

266
00:13:11,110 --> 00:13:12,110
to find Leader Yun as soon as possible.

267
00:13:12,230 --> 00:13:12,950
He went out?

268
00:13:13,110 --> 00:13:13,590
Yes,

269
00:13:13,700 --> 00:13:14,670
he left early in the morning.

270
00:13:14,750 --> 00:13:15,630
We don't know where he went.

271
00:13:16,070 --> 00:13:17,150
Tell them to stand by.

272
00:13:17,270 --> 00:13:17,830
I'll go look for him.

273
00:13:17,910 --> 00:13:18,470
Yes.

274
00:13:23,270 --> 00:13:24,630
Find him as soon as possible?

275
00:13:25,310 --> 00:13:26,830
Did something happen to his family?

276
00:13:28,050 --> 00:13:29,050
Where could he have gone?

277
00:13:38,390 --> 00:13:39,270
Ling Han.

278
00:13:48,270 --> 00:13:49,000
This is a place

279
00:13:49,020 --> 00:13:51,670
Ling Han never allows others to set foot in.

280
00:13:52,710 --> 00:13:53,990
Yun Hongshen believes

281
00:13:54,260 --> 00:13:55,670
he will definitely find

282
00:13:55,700 --> 00:13:57,270
something interesting here.

283
00:13:58,230 --> 00:13:59,150
Not the cipher key,

284
00:13:59,510 --> 00:14:02,190
not evidence of Ling Han framing Zhu He and Li Liang,

285
00:14:02,510 --> 00:14:04,670
but rather, Ling Han's hidden

286
00:14:04,790 --> 00:14:06,510
secrets that he doesn't want to reveal to others.

